Belgium’s Planning Bureau Cuts 2011, 2012 Inflation Forecasts

-- B y   J o h n   M a r t e n s
-- 
2011-10-04T08:41:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/belgium-s-planning-bureau-cuts-2011-2012-inflation-forecasts.html
Belgium ’s federal planning bureau cut
its forecast for the average increase in consumer prices to 3.4
percent from 3.5 percent for 2011 and to 1.8 percent from 2
percent for 2012, according to a statement posted on its
website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Martens at 
 jmartens1@bloomberg.net  